-channels-173805920.html">800 多个</a>FAST（ <a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/youtube-is-testing-a-hub-of-free-cable-style-channels-192518784.html">免费广告支持的流媒体电视）</a>频道阵容。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/google-tv-is-integrating-nfl-sunday-ticket-ahead-of-the-new-season-190358886.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/google-tv-is-integrating-nfl-sunday-ticket-ahead-of-the-new-season-190358886.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 4f6de6b1-8bb5-4c3a-848c-ccbf20804aeb</guid><dc:creator>威尔·尚克林</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 23 Aug 2023 19:03:58 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1692817439</ingested><modified> 2023-08-23T19:04:06+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[American Football]]></category><category><![CDATA[Sports & Recreation]]></category><category><![CDATA[National Football League]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Will Shanklin]]></category><media:content height="1686" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/927dc910-41e4-11ee-b7ff-1c475f38e65e" width="3000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1686" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/927dc910-41e4-11ee-b7ff-1c475f38e65e" width="3000"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Google]]></media:cre