e6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9Mb2dpdGVjaC1XaXJlbGVzcy1IZWFkc2V0LUJsYWNrLVRpY28vZHAvQjA4MTQxNUdDUy8_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMXFwLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJkOTgxYjIzNC1mYjg4LTQ5NzEtYWU2ZS0wZWYzOTkyMDY2YzIifQ&amp;signature=AQAAARpl47bt74ZcReVzngioCqqc3_wdaBi2uObTGW6mzEyK&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FLogitech-Wireless-Headset-Black-Tico%2Fdp%2FB081415GCS%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">Logitech G733</a> 。它听起来棒极了，电池续航时间超长，闪闪发光，前面有明亮的彩色 LED 灯条，还有可定制的织物头带。我用它和我的朋友在 Discord 上玩<em>龙与地下城</em>，以及偶尔录制播客。它已经问世几年了，但这仅仅意味着您可以在一些零售商处以低于 100 美元的价格购买这款耳机。如果它对您的血液来说仍然太丰富，请查看类似的<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAeVj9-cT5KYDJ1VzsgmeV90myzvkswmW_FtDecowGEHQ&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FLogitech-G435-Wireless-Gaming-Headset%2Fdp%2FB08R8GJPC2%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">G435</a> 。</p><h2>赛睿 Arctis Nova 1 </h2><p><core-commerce id="5797644451394652ad43e006f229d0d4" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>如果您正在寻找清晰的音频，SteelSeries 始终提供出色的清晰度和音量，而 Arctis 系列则以合理的价格提供这些服务。 <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAULvbItJ-94vWSfzUMkC0Dgq1IXohWHBtiY55cHoD8jf&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSteelSeries-Arctis-Multi-System-Gaming-Headset%2Fdp%2FB0B8Q4CR52%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">Nova 1</a>是一款有线<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-gaming-headset-130006477.html">游戏耳机</a>，由于其坚固的构造（我已经摔过两次了）、光滑的哑光表面以及柔软舒适的耳罩，一切都感觉很高级。它们可以阻挡较低的声音，但不能阻挡电视或哭闹的婴儿等声音，因此这款耳机非常适合新手父母。可调节麦克风是内置的，因此您也不必担心丢失。</p><h2>罗技 Zone Vibe 100 </h2><p><core-commerce id="04d1a4cf5c9f4318b95f4552f77536a3" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>自从大流行期间在家进行视频会议激增以来，我一直在称赞在所有商务会议中使用耳机的优点。它们可以阻挡不需要的噪音，使您的声音响亮而清晰，并且向其他人表明您正在通话。唯一的问题是游戏耳机看起来并不那么专业，但<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAQhmaAhYeybxj3grhjZXzGC59AUgpwYpwA6XTcFN1AXX&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FLogitech-Lightweight-Headphones-Microphone-Multipoint%2Fdp%2FB09NBX6BVW%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">Zone Vibe</a>却带来了一股新鲜空气。它提供罗技的所有专业知识，以时尚的无线套件提供可靠的游戏音频，让您在老板面前佩戴时不会感到尴尬。</p><h2>游戏键盘</h2><h2>海盗船 K60 RGB Pro 低调</h2><p><core-commerce id="229d7014b00b4b1ea9a2862062744578" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>当谈到购买键盘时，我的第一个建议总是“买海盗船”。 Corsair 键盘提供出色的打字体验，而且超级耐用。不幸的是，它们并不是最好的预算选择，因为它们相当昂贵，最便宜的通常要 120 美元。幸运的是，海盗船几年前推出了 K60 RGB Pro，对于那些习惯在笔记本电脑键盘上打字的人，我推荐<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9Db3JzYWlyLVByb2ZpbGUtTWVjaGFuaWNhbC1HYW1pbmctS2V5Ym9hcmQvZHAvQjA4SjZGQzNGMy8_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMXFwLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJkOTgxYjIzNC1mYjg4LTQ5NzEtYWU2ZS0wZWYzOTkyMDY2YzIifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAddgYWD0ZDVSiSlE7jGzBKhWNVarjgXhuT84-hOjEv6U&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FCorsair-Profile-Mechanical-Gaming-Keyboard%2Fdp%2FB08J6FC3F3%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">低调版本</a>。不，它与薄膜键盘不一样——它好得多，具有机械按键和耐用的结构，可以持续数年（以及数百甚至数千次游戏比赛）。</p><h2> HyperX Alloy Origins 60 </h2><p><core-commerce id="6f840b6bdba543349f446bfd0a94f3b8" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>游戏中最热门的新事物之一似乎是 60% 键盘，它砍掉了数字键盘，为桌面上腾出更多空间来放置鼠标或其他配件。较小也意味着它们往往也更便宜，因此精打细算的玩家应该考虑一下像<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9IeXBlclgtQWxsb3ktT3JpZ2lucy1NZWNoYW5pY2FsLUNvbXBhdGlibGUvZHAvQjA4WEJRNzlNTi8_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMXFwLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJkOTgxYjIzNC1mYjg4LTQ5NzEtYWU2ZS0wZWYzOTkyMDY2YzIifQ&amp;signature=AQAAARByhDlY6_lroxj3mU1gR12YCSINnm9D-0_mpa8_SdYk&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FHyperX-Alloy-Origins-Mechanical-Compatible%2Fdp%2FB08XBQ79MN%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">Alloy Origins 60</a>这样的牌组。除了体积小、价格实惠之外，它还坚如磐石。对于那些从全尺寸平台进行切换的人来说，右下角的箭头键位置应该不会那么混乱。</p><h2>赛睿 Apex TKL </h2><p><core-commerce id="cd4faa772d6d41d1878170514996bb49" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>机械键盘很棒，但即使是最安静的机械键盘对于某些环境来说也可能太吵了。 <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9TdGVlbFNlcmllcy1Db21wYWN0LU1lY2hhbmljYWwtR2FtaW5nLUtleWJvYXJkL2RwL0IwN1RHUTdDTkY_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMXFwLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJkOTgxYjIzNC1mYjg4LTQ5NzEtYWU2ZS0wZWYzOTkyMDY2YzIifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAT1p52opLHFyBqloQzp67ZTl2VfRatEWCkioQK2y8V-m&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSteelSeries-Compact-Mechanical-Gaming-Keyboard%2Fdp%2FB07TGQ7CNF" class="rapid-with-clickid">Apex TKL</a>非常擅长低调：它是 60% 的面板，因此结构紧凑，其按键提供出色的打字响应，同时非常安静。 Apex TKL 比许多其他避开数字键盘的键盘要大一点，但这是有充分理由的 - 您会欣赏专用的箭头键和音量滚轮，后者是任何使用键盘的人的必备工具。他们的设备上有很多媒体。</p><h2>游戏鼠标</h2><h2>罗技G305 </h2><p><core-commerce id="ec6a27931be34a9bac6cac5483b21fe5" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>预算有限并不意味着您必须在质量或外观上吝啬， <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAUK_87bq92__IfsIqBabB7rSdGpKvmt92f6yIf15THi5&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FLogitech-LIGHTSPEED-Wireless-Gaming-Mouse%2Fdp%2FB07CMS5Q6P%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">G305</a>是一款高性能且时尚的鼠标。同样好的一点是它让事情变得简单，有六个可编程按钮和时尚的外形。电池续航时间额定为 250 小时，不过根据我个人的使用情况，我发誓它的续航时间要长得多，而且它只需要一节 AAA 电池，因此您可以在几秒钟内更换它并重新开始游戏。如果您有 G435 这样的耳机，您可以购买淡紫色的 G305 来搭配，或者只选择基本的黑色型号。如果您想节省更多钱并且不介意使用有线鼠标，还可以查看我们在<a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-gaming-mouse-140004638.html">最佳游戏鼠标购买指南</a>中推荐的<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAX8wOHY1cw5s-StlQN2xouTR85xvTyGMrQYz-L-SN2NP&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB07YN82X3B%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">G203 Lightspeed</a> 。</p><h2>赛睿 Aerox 3 </h2><p><core-commerce id="4118b9eddeba41a4b5b64ef1ca225517" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>每个游戏玩家都知道一两次将东西洒在桌子上的痛苦，无论是水、咖啡还是苏打水。 <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAdncd-RI2DxSMNlxZf_ex8r_4HySUvmzbmeju6V7sG27&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSteelSeries-Aerox-Ultra-Lightweight-Resistant-connectivity%2Fdp%2FB0966VYKG3%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">Aerox 3</a>可能看起来像是正在走向灾难，因为它身上有很多漏洞。但它实际上的防护等级为 IP54，这意味着它可以承受良好的溅水并继续工作（尽管如果不擦拭的话可能会有点粘）。这些孔不仅看起来很酷，而且还使鼠标握起来更轻（如果您喜欢的话），并且可以防止热量在您的手掌中积聚。</p><h2> SteelSeries Rival 3 无线</h2><p><core-commerce id="6bd45496665b4c3fa0d4fa3a6b41c084" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>如果您正在寻找更传统但价格实惠且无线的产品， <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:14;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAURb9N8tQZBHkaC3DiKT91dZVDQpxZE3mhAvbxw4Vyr5&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSteelSeries-Rival-Wireless-Gaming-Mouse%2Fdp%2FB08GB2PF71" class="rapid-with-clickid">Rival 3</a>可能正适合您。这是一款基本的黑色鼠标，具有时尚的轮廓和五个可编程按钮。它配备了无线接收器以确保强大的连接，而且还可以通过蓝牙工作，因此您可以轻松地将其切换到笔记本电脑或移动设备。这使得它非常适合办公室和游戏，是终极省钱工具。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/best-budget-gaming-accessories-130040522.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/best-budget-gaming-accessories-130040522.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> d981b234-fb88-4971-ae6e-0ef3992066c2</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·诺杜斯</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 23 Aug 2023 17:50:05 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1692813006</ingested><modified> 2023-08-23T17:50:19+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Shopping]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Naudus]]></category><media:content height="1080" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/9cbf38a0-24a7-11ee-bb51-b15691920837" width="1616"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1080" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/9cbf38a0-24a7-11ee-bb51-b15691920837" width="1616"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Photo by Kris Naudus / Engadget]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[The best budget gaming accessories]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[The best budget gaming accessories]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[WhatsApp lets you create groups without naming them]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> WhatsApp 现在允许您创建小组，而无需先命名。马克·扎克伯格在<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.facebook.com/zuck/posts/pfbid052GAV4iPYPPYzvtDQomkyFD9hWjW8HeM5vKzS7gH2g3kc26Qd2QZxMUyTRTUyh1pl">Facebook 帖子</a>中宣布了这一新功能（<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://techcrunch.com/2023/08/23/whatsapp-groups-without-names/">来自</a><em>TechCrunch</em> ）。以前，您在设置时必须选择组的名称。</p><p> <em>TechCrunch</em>报道称，未命名群组的成员上限为 6 名，而命名群组的成员上限为 1,024 人。此外，据报道，WhatsApp 将根据未命名群组的成员自动生成占位符名称。 （例如，下面的扎克伯格示例图片中，“Rocco &amp; Li-Chen”代表他们之间的聊天。）根据他们保存成员联系人的方式，每个成员的群组名称也会有所不同。 </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/d10309d0-41d9-11ee-afbd-7becbb688d6a" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/d10309d0-41d9-11ee-afbd-7becbb688d6a" style="height:540px;width:960px;" alt="马克·扎克伯格分享的屏幕截图，显示带有群组标题的 WhatsApp 通知" data-uuid="a598fad5-9eaf-34b1-9e9f-a90b6e9562cb"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">元/马克·扎克伯格</div></figure><p>据报道，当加入一个包含未保存您的联系人的人员的未命名群组时，它会向该群组显示您的电话号码。这表明该功能更多是为已建立的朋友、家人或同事设计的，而不是为陌生人设计的。</p><p> <em>TechCrunch</em>报道称，该功能将“在未来几周内”在全球推出。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/whatsapp-lets-you-create-groups-without-naming-them-174420165.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/whatsapp-lets-you-create-groups-without-naming-them-174420165.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> b79f4d07-8415-4a72-948e-53d78c59c6af</guid><dc:creator>威尔·尚克林</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 23 Aug 2023 17:44:20 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1692814447</ingested><modified> 2023-08-23T18:14:14+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Personal Investing Ideas & Strategies]]></category><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Will Shanklin]]></category><media:content height="2628" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-02/3e057150-b2cc-11ed-97dd-5931ea7e4cad" width="4000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="2628" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-02/3e057150-b2cc-11ed-97dd-5931ea7e4cad" width="4000"><media